name: Appcues Events
body:
#### Friday, Jan 23

*6-7pm — Networking*
Pizza and beer provided by local sponsors.

*7pm — Contest officially starts*

*7-12am — Hacking begins*

#### Saturday, Jan 24

*10am — Doors open*
Coffee provided. Hack from home earlier if you are too excited to sleep.

*10am-7pm — Hack*
Start shipping.

*7-8pm — Break for dinner*
You are on your own to forage for food.

*8pm-12am — Hack*

*12am — Doors close*

#### Sunday, Jan 25

*10am — Doors open*
Coffee provided, again.

*10am-7pm — Hack*
Start shipping.

*7pm — Contest officially ends*

*7-8pm — Presentations*
What good is a hackathon if you don’t get to share what you built? We’ll each talk about our projects and we can even secretly vote for which ones will win certain categories.
